window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the club, with flashing lights and loud music, seeing him across the room is a scene out of a movie.</p> <p>We lock eyes and sway to the beat—instantly connecting.</p> <p>He nudges his head, calling me to the other side. Me? Of all the women in the club, this sexy man wants me to join him in VIP.</p> <p>So I do.</p> <p>And then I realize how tall he is, and the other guys surrounding him are also.</p> <p>Wait. This guy was on the basketball court at the game I watched the night before. The guys standing around him are his teammates on the Houston Outlaws.</p> <p>And me? I'm a small-town girl with a class of fifth graders, only in LA for a few more nights. So you could imagine my answer when he asks, \"Wanna come back to the room with me?\"</p>"; 
